	 East Bengal were shot out for 282 against BNR in a semi-final match of the AN Ghosh Trophy at the JU, Salt Lake Campus ground on Tuesday.       
	Parthasarathi Bhattacharya scored 85. Mannu Kumar contributed with an unbeaten 73. BNRs Sourav Roy picked up five wickets.      
